
Native serial library for using the footswitch in COM-port mode

See INSTALL for installation instructions (Written by Trent Jarvi, author of the rxtx library)


Linux/Solaris:

The user running the yada client must be a member of the group "uucp" to be able 
to write a lock file to the /var/lock directory and a member of the group "tty" 
to have access to the serial port.
